  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spectralogic.ds3client.helpers.pagination.SpectraS3PaginationLoader<T,E,F>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type returned by the iterator
    E - The AbstractPaginationRequest this loader will invoke

    LazyIterable.LazyLoader<T>

    public class SpectraS3PaginationLoader<T,E extends AbstractPaginationRequest,F extends AbstractPaginationResponse>
extends java.lang.Object
implements LazyIterable.LazyLoader<T>
    This class is used as the base implementation for all Spectra S3 paginating calls. It requires a PaginatingCommand which implements the call specific logic for each paginated request.
